<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Boshqaruv Paneli</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" 
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" 
          integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA==" 
          crossorigin="anonymous" 
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
          
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #6a11cb;
            --secondary-color: #2575fc;
            --success-color: #2ecc71;
            --danger-color: #e74c3c;
            --background-light: #f4f4f4;
            --card-background: #ffffff;
            --link-color: #3498db;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-light);
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .dashboard-container { 
            width: 90%; 
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 50px auto; 
            background: var(--card-background); 
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); 
        }

        h1 {
            color: var(--primary-color); 
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-color); 
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.2em;
        }
        
        /* Statistik Kartalar */
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .stat-card {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .stat-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .stat-card p {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
        }

        /* Boshqaruv Tugmalari (Navigation Grid) */
        .module-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }
        .module-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: var(--card-background);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--link-color); /* Vertikal chiziq */
        }
        .module-link:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        .module-link i {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .module-text h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #333;
        }
        .module-text p {
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }

        /* Profil va Logout */
        .profile-actions {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .profile-actions a {
            color: var(--link-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .profile-actions button {
            background: var(--danger-color);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .profile-actions button:hover {
            background: #c0392b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-container">
        <h1>Admin Boshqaruv Paneli üëë</h1>

        <h2>Xush kelibsiz, <%= user.first_name %>!</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #555;">Tizimni boshqarish va nazorat qilish uchun quyidagi modullardan foydalaning.</p>
        
        <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; color: #3498db;">üìä Umumiy Statistika</h2>
        
        <div class="stats-grid">
            
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>Jami Xodimlar</h3>
                <p><%= stats.totalEmployees || 0 %></p> 
            </div>
            
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>Fakultetlar</h3>
                <p><%= stats.totalFaculties || 0 %></p> 
            </div>
            
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>Jami Talabalar</h3>
                <p><%= stats.totalStudents|| 0 %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>Jami Kurslar</h3>
                <p><%= stats.totalCourses || 0 %></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 style="margin-top: 40px; color: #3498db;">üõ†Ô∏è Boshqaruv Modullari</h2>
        
        <div class="module-grid">
            
            <a href="/employees" class="module-link" style="border-left-color: #e67e22;">
                <i class="fas fa-users" style="color: #e67e22;"></i>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <h3>Xodimlar</h3>
                    <p>Barcha xodimlarni (Admin/Teacher) boshqarish.</p>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="/admin/faculties" class="module-link" style="border-left-color: #9b59b6;">
                <i class="fas fa-building" style="color: #9b59b6;"></i>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <h3>Fakultetlar</h3>
                    <p>Fakultetlarni yaratish, tahrirlash va o'chirish.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/admin/courses" class="module-link" style="border-left-color: #1abc9c;">
                <i class="fas fa-book-open" style="color: #1abc9c;"></i>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <h3>Kurslar</h3>
                    <p>Kurslarni boshqarish (yaratilmagan).</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/admin/students" class="module-link" style="border-left-color: #3498db;">
                <i class="fas fa-user-graduate" style="color: #3498db;"></i>
                <div class="module-text">
                    <h3>Talabalar</h3>
                    <p>Talabalarni ro'yxatga olish (yaratilmagan).</p>
                </div>
            </a>

        </div>

        <div class="profile-actions">
            <a href="/employees/profile"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i> Mening Profilim</a>
            
            <form action="/employees/logout" method="POST" style="display: inline;">
                <button type="submit"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Tizimdan chiqish</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>